<h4 id="test-and-examination">Test and examination</h4>
<p>The test is a tool to measure the knowledge level of your students and adjust
the learning material accordingly. An exam or the examination is more formal and
it tells you if a students passed or failed a class or course.</p>

<h4 id="point-of-view-and-perspective">Point of view and perspective</h4>
<p>Point of view: focuses on the type of narrator used to tell the story.</p>
